         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>On the auspicious day when the Jovian year Rāvuttiri, the month of Aṟppaci, the 10th
               day, Saturday, the eighth lunar day, the [constellation of] Tiruvōṇam come together,
               the Āḻvārpirapantam, which was studied by Veṅkiṭācam, was fully copied and
               completed</p>
         </div>
